                        <h1 class="hero-title">Volunteer With Us</h1>
                        <p class="hero-subtitle">Transform lives through your time and care</p>
                        <p class="hero-description">
                            Join our community of dedicated volunteers who are making a real difference in the lives 
                            of street children. Whether you have an hour a week or a day a month, your contribution matters.
                        </p>
                        <div class="hero-stats">
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
                                <span class="stat-label">Active Volunteers</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <span class="stat-number">Weekly</span>
